e4bt. Pfarreien durch Predigt und disziplinar. Verf\u00fcgungen (u.a. Entlassung von Konkubinatspriestern). 1588 verbot er fremden Solddienst."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q50379049", "itemLabel": "Q50379049", "dhsid": "021745", "namefr": "", "articlefr": "", "namede": "Joachim Opser", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joachim_Opser", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "Joachim Opser", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joachim_Opser", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "119476428"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q50379049", "wikipedia_page_title": "Joachim Opser", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "O", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/021745/2010-10-19"}